ourceFileGenerator#BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.ModSourceFileGenerator.Generate(System.Text.StringBuilder,string).sb\" title=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.ModSourceFileGenerator.Generate(System.Text.StringBuilder, string).sb\">sb</a> for the class</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-csharp\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">virtual</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">Generate</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\">System.Text.StringBuilder sb, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">ref</span> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">string</span> fileName</span>)</span>;\n</code></pre>\n<h4 id=\"parameters\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"position-relative\" href=\"#parameters\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Parameters</h4>\n<p><a name=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.ModSourceFileGenerator.Generate(System.Text.StringBuilder,string).sb\"></a></p>\n<p><code class=\"hljs\">sb</code> <a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/api/System.Text.StringBuilder\" title=\"System.Text.StringBuilder\">System.Text.StringBuilder</a></p>\n<p><a name=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.ModSourceFileGenerator.Generate(System.Text.StringBuilder,string).fileName\"></a></p>\n<p><code class=\"hljs\">fileName</code> <a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/api/System.String\" title=\"System.String\">System.String</a></p>\n<p><a name=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.ModSourceFileGenerator.Generate(System.Text.StringBuilder)\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"modsourcefilegeneratorgeneratestringbuilder-method\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"position-relative\" href=\"#modsourcefilegeneratorgeneratestringbuilder-method\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>ModSourceFileGenerator.Generate(StringBuilder) Method</h2>\n<p>Append the file's contents to <a href=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.ModSourceFileGenerator#BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.ModSourceFileGenerator.Generate(System.Text.StringBuilder).sb\" title=\"BTD_Mod_Helper.Api.Mod